The noblest utterance upon Tawhid (the doctrine of Unity) is the
saying of Abu Bakr as-Siddiqï¼š 'Glory be to Him who hath made for His
creatures no means of attaining unto Knowledge of Him save through
their impotence to attain (in themselves) unto that Knowledge!'
